{"type":"message","id":"682ee84c","parentId":"9602778e","timestamp":"2026-02-27T06:20:29.520Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"functions.browser:19","toolName":"browser","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"browser\",\n  \"error\": \"Can't reach the OpenClaw browser control service. Restart the OpenClaw gateway (OpenClaw.app menubar, or `openclaw gateway`). Do NOT retry the browser tool — it will keep failing. Use an alternative approach or inform the user that the browser is currently unavailable. (Error: Error: Element \\\"e410\\\" not found or not visible. Run a new snapshot to see current page elements.)\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"browser","error":"Can't reach the OpenClaw browser control service. Restart the OpenClaw gateway (OpenClaw.app menubar, or `openclaw gateway`). Do NOT retry the browser tool — it will keep failing. Use an alternative approach or inform the user that the browser is currently unavailable. (Error: Error: Element \"e410\" not found or not visible. Run a new snapshot to see current page elements.)"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772173229515}}
{"type":"message","id":"23977268","parentId":"682ee84c","timestamp":"2026-02-27T06:21:16.806Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"草，还是不行。browser 控制服务确实有问题——snapshot 能跑，但 act 操作一直失败。\n\n**现状总结：**\n- ✅ 成功进入帖子详情页（刘畅_Ella 的领证帖子）\n- ✅ 成功输入评论：\"祝福你们！30岁领证这个节奏很稳，先磨合再绑定，理性又浪漫\"\n- ❌ **无法点击发送按钮** — browser act 操作持续报错\n\n**错误信息：** \"Can't reach the OpenClaw browser control service\"\n\n按照 cursor 哥写的 skill，这时候应该由你来重启 gateway：\n```\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n或者你也可以直接在浏览器里手动点击发送按钮（评论已经输入好了，就在页面底部）。\n\n要我继续尝试其他方法，还是你先重启一下 gateway？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":143452,"output":160,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":143612,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772173229521}}
