{"type":"message","id":"8a87ee15","parentId":"b65efa44","timestamp":"2026-02-27T06:32:26.465Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好，现在我看到了！滚动到底部后，compact snapshot 里显示：\n\n- `text: 说点什么...` —— 占位文本\n- `button \"发送\" [ref=e141] [disabled]` —— 发送按钮（disabled）\n- `button \"取消\" [ref=e142]`\n\n但「说点什么...」还是纯文本，没有 ref。这说明**评论输入框可能是一个不可交互的元素**，或者需要用特殊方式激活。\n\n让我试试用 JavaScript 直接操作 DOM 来找到并点击评论输入区域："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.browser:34","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","request":{"kind":"evaluate","fn":"() => { \n  // 查找所有包含\"说点什么\"的元素\n  const allElements = document.querySelectorAll('*');\n  for (let el of allElements) {\n    if (el.textContent && el.textContent.includes('说点什么') && el.children.length === 0) {\n      // 找到文本节点，尝试点击其父元素\n      let parent = el.parentElement;\n      while (parent && !parent.onclick && !parent.getAttribute('role')) {\n        parent = parent.parentElement;\n      }\n      if (parent) {\n        parent.click();\n        return 'Clicked comment area';\n      }\n    }\n  }\n  return 'Comment area not found';\n}"}}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":151968,"output":299,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":152267,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772173903352}}
